<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="temper-n">temper <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tempə(r)/    美 /'tempər/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>脾气；心情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>lose / control one’s temper</strong>
发/控制脾气</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>good-tempered / bad-tempered</strong>
脾气好的/不好的</p></div></div>